Q print the list of actor 
actor = ["srk ", "salman", "akshay", "dhoni", "kohli", "gill", "rishabh pant"]

list = 0
while list < len(actor):
    print(actor[list])
    list += 1
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Break and continue loops 

--------------------------------------
range into loops
for i in range (10):
    print(i)
output would be 0 to 9
----------------------------------------
print odd and even nnumber in loops (range)
odd
for i in range(1, 101, 2):
    print(i)
even 
for i in range(0, 101, 2):
    print(i)
---------------------------------------------
print the table of any number by input and loops

n = int(input("enter the number : "))

for i in range (1, 11):
    print(n * i )
--------------------------------------------------
Pass statement in loops
pass used when we want to use null value (syntax)

for i in range (15):
    pass
print(some useful work)
----------------------------------------
total of range of numbers :
n = 6
sum = 0
for i in range (1, n+1):
    sum += i
    
print("total sum =",  sum)  
----------------------------------------
find the n number of factorial 
n = 3
fact = 1

for i in range(1, n+1):
    fact *= i

print("factorial number =", fact)
